OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny daytime
OL,6,Fshowers will quickly clear this
OL,7,Fevening to leave a dry night with some
OL,8,Fclear spells. Under the clearer skies
OL,9,Fand light winds a few mist and fog
OL,10,Fpatches forming towards dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FDry with sunny spells at
OL,13,Ffirst. Cloud will build through the
OL,14,Fafternoon, perhaps with the odd spot
OL,15,Fof light rain. Temperatures around
OL,16,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
